00:12:51,061 --> 00:12:52,396
Grandpa.

131
00:12:52,813 --> 00:12:53,772
Hey?

132
00:12:53,856 --> 00:12:56,150
Max, let's go upstairs, huh?

133
00:12:56,859 --> 00:12:59,028
[Max] I'm fine
right here, Annie.

