175
00:16:08,884 --> 00:16:10,719
I failed my wife...

176
00:16:12,096 --> 00:16:13,097
[exhales]

177
00:16:13,180 --> 00:16:14,181
I...

178
00:16:14,264 --> 00:16:15,808
failed my family.

179
00:16:18,352 --> 00:16:20,270
I failed myself.

180
00:16:26,402 --> 00:16:27,987
[microphone feedback]

181
00:16:48,424 --> 00:16:50,217
You said something
to... that...

182
00:16:51,510 --> 00:16:54,013
