to a room full of strangers?

213
00:18:02,539 --> 00:18:03,791
Enough!

214
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:17,554
[Annie] I got it, I got it.

215
00:18:17,638 --> 00:18:18,722
[door slams]

216
00:18:24,728 --> 00:18:25,979
[Max] Annie.

217
00:18:27,856 --> 00:18:29,733
